Concept: A clean, focused input form.

Input Field: Large numeric keypad-style input for the amount at the top ($0.00).

Category Selector: Horizontal scrolling icons (🍔 Food, 🚗 Transport, 🛍️ Shopping).

Date Picker: Defaulted to "Today."

Note Field: "What was this for?" placeholder.

Primary Button: A large, high-contrast "Save Expense" button at the bottom.
